    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "A wonderful opportunity to own a reliable, well-maintained vehicle that's ready to hit the road! This car presents beautifully \u2014 the exterior shows only light, everyday wear you'd expect from a well-loved vehicle, with no major dents or damage to speak of. The interior is clean and comfortable, and the mechanicals are in great working order, giving you confidence for your daily commute or weekend adventures. If you're looking for a dependable car that's been genuinely cared for without paying mint-condition prices, this one deserves a serious look!",
      "price": 33500.0,
