    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Reliable & Road-Ready \u2013 A Great Everyday Car at a Honest Price! \ud83d\ude97\n\nIf you're looking for a dependable vehicle that's been well cared for, this is a great opportunity! This car is in good condition \u2014 it runs smoothly, looks presentable, and has been maintained with care. You'll notice it drives confidently and comfortably, making it a solid choice for daily commutes or weekend adventures.\n\nNo surprises here \u2014 just a genuinely good car at a fair price. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself! \ud83d\ude4c",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Calling all DIY mechanics and project car enthusiasts \u2014 here's your next opportunity! This vehicle is being sold as-is in poor condition, meaning it has notable mechanical issues and visible wear that will require attention before regular use. That said, it's a real chance to get your hands on a car at a very accessible price point and make it your own. If you've got the skills and the vision, this one could be a rewarding project \u2014 come take a look and see the potential for yourself!",
      "price": 3500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a poor-condition car that needs significant work. The exterior shows heavy wear including noticeable rust, dents, and faded or damaged paint in multiple areas. The interior is worn with torn upholstery, cracked trim, and general deterioration throughout. Mechanically, the car has known issues and will require repairs \u2014 it is best suited for a buyer who is a hands-on DIYer, a mechanic looking for a project, or someone seeking parts. Do not expect a reliable daily driver without substantial investment. Priced accordingly to reflect the true condition.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is offered as a reliable, drivable used car with honest acknowledgment of its wear and imperfections. The exterior shows multiple scratches, a few small dents, and some fading paint consistent with its age and use \u2014 nothing that affects drivability, but noticeable upon close inspection. Mechanically, the car runs and drives as expected for its age, though buyers should anticipate that some components may require attention or replacement in the near future. The interior shows moderate wear including worn upholstery, some scuffs on trim panels, and minor staining. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and steering \u2014 are functional. This is a solid choice for a buyer seeking an affordable, usable vehicle who understands they are purchasing a car that has lived a normal life and shows it. No major hidden issues, just honest everyday wear.",
      "price": 15000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition, and we want to be fully upfront with prospective buyers about what that means. The exterior shows significant wear, including multiple dents, scratches, and areas of rust or paint deterioration that are clearly visible. The interior has seen heavy use, with worn or torn upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general wear throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car requires attention \u2014 buyers should anticipate repair or maintenance work to bring it to reliable daily-driver status, and a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic is strongly recommended. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer who is handy with repairs, looking for a project car, or needs basic transportation and is prepared for the associated upkeep. Priced accordingly to reflect its current state honestly.",
      "price": 7500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    }
